<statement><div><p>Evaluate <m> \displaystyle \sqrt{z}</m> given that <m>z={0} + {4}i</m>.</p> 
<p>Note:</p>
<p/><ol>
  <li><p style="color:blue">Give all the roots!</p></li>
  <li><p style="color:blue">You might want to write <m>z</m> in polar form first, with your solution in <m>\pi</m> radians, or in the form <m>\displaystyle z=re^{i\theta}</m> to simplify the calculations.</p></li>
</ol>
